data.description: Check out this updated home in a fantastic location. Just down the street from Adams Elementary, Banner Medical Center and close to shopping.  This home features two large living areas with an additional flex space in the back that is currently used as a gym. Plank flooring throughout the home with updated baths. Brand new HVAC installed July 2023. Take a look at the kitchen with two large islands providing tons of additional storage. Large added patio addition in the back with grass is the perfect for gatherings and relaxation. Low maintenance front yard with added pavers just waiting for your personal touch. Don't miss this great opportunity in Mesa.
